elements.description:
Verify that when "Tipo de Depositante" is selected as 
              "Demandante", the "Depositante" field displays all 
              registered Demandante names.
elements.name: Verify "Depositante" Field for "Demandante" Selection

steps.name: Launch the URL
Enter Username
Tap on Next button
Enter password of user
Tap on SignIn button
User select Yes Option
I am on Servicios Secretariales Option
I should see the Servicios Secretariales Page
I Click on Search Dropdown Button
I click on tribunal dropdown
I see the dropdown and select the option
I go for date fecha selection
I select the date for fecha
I click on Search Icon
I click On Tramitar Button to move into next page
I should verify the parte button is enable or not
I should see the Doctmentos and click on it
I click On More option view Button
